Package com.example.crowdtest.ui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EditUserFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener
    Fragment listener interface for when OK is pressed
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinomialActivity
    Binomial experiment activity class that has two buttons for submitting success and failure
    CountActivity
    Count experiment activity class
    CreateExperimentActivity
    Activity for creating a new experiment, uses different fragments to put together a new Experiment object
    EditUserFragment
    Fragment to collect contact information in the UserProfileActivity
    ExpDetailsFragment
    Fragment to collect experiment information in the CreateExperimentActivity
    ExperimentActivity
    The general activity class for all the experiment activities
    ExperimentListActivity
    Display the owned and subscribed experiments associated to the signed in user.
    GeolocationToggleFragment
    Fragment for the final stage (geolocation toggle) of experiment creation and publishing the experiment to the database
    MainActivity
    Main Activity class
    NewExpFragment
    Fragment for choosing which type of experiment is made
    PagerAdapter
    Page adapter for tabbed view of ExperimentListActivity
    SearchExperimentActivity
    Activity to view all experiments and search for those containing a user-specified keyword Long clicking experiments open context menu
    SubscribedExpFragment
    Fragment to display the experiments signed in user is subscribed to in the ExperimentListActivity
    UserProfileActivity
    Activity for viewing the user profile, uses a fragment to allow for editing of contact information in the UserProfile object
    ValueInputActivity
    Value input experiment activity class.
